This script reading was entirely composed of a group of young actors from Beijing, who rehearsed for two weeks under the leadership of director Tang Wei. Each of them created a character biography in order to analyze the characters in depth, in the hope that after nearly 40 years, after re-examination, this masterpiece of realistic drama will regain its charm.
